 & Punishment]]'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"8\" | [[The WB]]\n! Fall\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"3\" | [[Ripley's Believe It or Not! (TV series)#Second revival (2000%E2%80%932003)|Ripley's Believe It or Not!]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[The Steve Harvey Show]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | '''[[Men, Women & Dogs]]'''\n| [[Nikki (TV series)|Nikki]]\n| '''[[Off Centre]]'''\n| style=\"background:#abbfff;\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"8\" | Local Programming\n|-\n! Follow Up\n| rowspan=\"4\" | [[Off Centre]]\n| [[Nikki (TV series)|Nikki]]\n|-\n! December\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Nikki (TV series)|Nikki]]\n| [[Men, Women & Dogs]]\n|-\n! Winter\n| [[The Steve Harvey Show]]\n| [[The Steve Harvey Show]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | '''[[The Jamie Kennedy Experiment]]'''\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[For Your Love (TV series)|For Your Love]]\n|-\n! Spring\n| colspan=\"2\" | '''[[No Boundaries (TV series)|No Boundaries]]'''\n| [[The Jamie Kennedy Experiment]]\n|-\n! Follow Up\n| colspan=\"4\" rowspan=\"2\" | Flix From the Frog\n| [[The Jamie Kennedy Experiment]]\n| [[Off Centre]]\n|-\n! Summer\n| rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\" | [[Angel (1999 TV series)|Angel]]\n|-\n! Follow Up\n| [[For Your Love (TV series)|For Your Love]]\n| [[For Your Love (TV series)|For Your Love]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Charmed]]\n|}\n\nNOTE: FOX aired 2 episodes of '''[[The Chamber (game show)|The Chamber]]''' in mid-January 2002. During the fall, ''Futurama'' and ''King of the Hill'' were preempted by overruns of NFL games. On The WB, ''Lost in the USA'' was supposed to air at 7-8, but it was cancelled due to 9/11 problems.\n\n== Monday ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;margin-right:0;text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| Network\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:30 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:30 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; 