ries)|24]]'''\n|-\n! Spring\n| '''[[Andy Richter Controls the Universe]]'''\n|-\n! Summer\n| Family guy \n| colspan=\"2\" | '''[[American Idol]]'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"7\" |[[NBC]]\n! Fall\n| '''[[Emeril (TV series)|Emeril]]'''\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Three Sisters (TV series)|Three Sisters]]\n| style=\"background:#0ff;\" rowspan=\"7\"| [[Frasier]] (#14/9.9)<br/><small>(Tied with ''[[JAG (TV series)|JAG]]'')</small>\n| rowspan=\"7\" | '''[[Scrubs (TV series)|Scrubs]]'''\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"7\" | [[Dateline NBC|Dateline Tuesday]]\n|-\n! Winter\n| '''[[Imagine That (TV series)|Imagine That]]'''\n|-\n! Follow-up\n| [[ Frasier]]\n|-\n! Spring\n| [[Frasier]] repeats\n| '''[[Watching Ellie]]'''\n|-\n! May\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Frasier]] repeats and NBC Specials\n|-\n! Summer\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Spy TV]]\n| [[Scrubs (TV series)|Scrubs]]\n|-\n! August\n| '''[[The Rerun Show]]'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"4\" |[[UPN]]\n! Fall\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"4\" | [[Buffy the Vampire Slayer]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Roswell (TV series)|Roswell]]\n| style=\"background:#abbfff;\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"5\" | Local Programming\n|-\n! Spring\n| '''[[As If (U.S. TV series)|As If]]'''\n| '''[[The Random Years]]'''\n|-\n! Follow-up\n| colspan=\"2\" | Roswell \n|-\n! Late Spring\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Roswell (TV series)|Roswell]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" | [[The WB]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Gilmore Girls]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | '''[[Smallville]]'''\n|}\n\nNote: ''[[Buffy the Vampire Slayer]]'' and ''[[Roswell (TV series)|Roswell]]'' moved to [[UPN]] from [[The WB Television Network|The WB]] this season.\n\n== Wednesday ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;margin-right:0;text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| Network\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:30 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:30 P