e to 9/11 problems.\n\n== Monday ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;margin-right:0;text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| Network\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:30 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:30 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 10:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 10:30 PM\n|-\n! rowspan=\"4\"| [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]\n! Fall\n| rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\" | [[Who Wants to Be a Millionaire (U.S. game show)|Who Wants to Be a Millionaire]]\n| [[Monday Night Football|NFL Monday Showcase]]\n| style=\"background:#ff0;\" colspan=\"3\"| [[Monday Night Football]] (#7/11.5)\n|-\n! Winter\n| colspan=\"4\" | [[The ABC Monday Night Movie]]\n|-\n! Spring\n| [[My Wife and Kids]] \n| [[The Wayne Brady Show]]\n| colspan=\"2\"| The Practice \n| rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Once and Again]]\n|-\n! Follow-up\n| colspan=\"2\"| [[America's Funniest Home Videos]]\n| colspan=\"2\"| '''[[The Bachelor (U.S. TV series)|The Bachelor]]'''\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" | [[CBS]]\n! Fall\n| style=\"background:#0ff;\"| [[The King of Queens]] (#19/8.9)\n| style=\"background:#0ff;\"| [[Yes, Dear]] (#20/8.8)<br/><small>(Tied with ''[[Crossing Jordan]]'')</small>\n| style=\"background:#ff0;\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[Everybody Loves Raymond]] (#4/12.8)\n| style=\"background:#0ff;\" rowspan=\"3\"| [[Becker (TV series)|Becker]] (#11/10.7)\n| style=\"background:#f0f;\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[Family Law (TV series)|Family Law]] (#30/7.7)<br/><small>(Tied with ''[[60 Minutes II]]'')</small>\n|-\n! Spring\n| style=\"background:#0ff;\"| [[Yes, Dear]] (#20/8.8)<br/><small>(Tied with ''[[Crossing Jordan]]'')</small>\n| style=\"background:#f0f;\"| '''[[Baby Bob]]''' (#25/8.1)<br/><small>(Tied with ''[[Dateline NBC]]'' \u2013 Fri