ow-Up\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Popstars]]\n|-\n! Winter\n| colspan=\"2\" | Various Repeats\n|-\n! March\n| [[My Guide to Becoming a Rock Star]]\n| [[My Guide to Becoming a Rock Star]]\n|-\n! Spring\n| colspan=\"2\" | Various Repeats and Specials\n|}\n\n== Friday ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;margin-right:0;text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| Network\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 8:30 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 9:30 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 10:00 PM\n! style=\"background:silver; text-align:center;\"| 10:30 PM\n|-\n! rowspan=\"6\"| [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]\n! Fall\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[The Mole (U.S. season 2)|The Mole II: The Next Betrayal]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\" | '''[[Thieves (TV series)|Thieves]]'''\n| rowspan=\"3\" colspan=\"2\" | [[Once and Again]]\n|-\n! Follow-up\n| rowspan=\"5\" colspan=\"2\" | [[America's Funniest Home Videos]]\n|-\n! December\n| colspan=\"2\" | ABC Specials\n|-\n! Winter\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[Once and Again]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | Vanished\n|-\n! Follow-up\n| colspan=\"2\" | Various programming\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[20/20 (U.S. TV series)|20/20]]\n|-\n! Mid-Summer\n| [[Whose Line Is It Anyway? (U.S. TV series)|Whose Line Is It Anyway?]]\n| [[Whose Line Is It Anyway? (U.S. TV series)|Whose Line Is It Anyway?]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"7\" |[[CBS]]\n! Fall\n| rowspan=\"2\" | '''[[The Ellen Show]]'''\n| '''[[Danny (TV series)|Danny]]'''\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"3\" | [[That's Life (2000 TV series)|That's Life]]\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"6\" | [[48 Hours (TV series)|48 Hours]]\n|-\n! Follow-up\n| Yes dear \n|-\n! November\n| The king of queens \n| [[The Ellen Show]]\n|-\n! January\n| colspan=\"2\" | [[JAG (TV series)|JAG]] repeats\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"3