sworth]]\n|align=center|4\n|align=center style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"|5\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1985 Indianapolis 500|1985]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center|15\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"|8\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1986 Indianapolis 500|1986]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"|3\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"|6\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1987 Indianapolis 500|1987]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center|9\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|29\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1988 Indianapolis 500|1988]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center|10\n|align=center style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"|4\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1989 Indianapolis 500|1989]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=center|21\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|17\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1990 Indianapolis 500|1990]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=center|5\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|20\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1991 Indianapolis 500|1991]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=center|5\n|align=center style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"|2\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1992 Indianapolis 500|1992]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Ford-Cosworth]]\n|align=center|6\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|''13''\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1994 Indianapolis 500|1994]]\n| [[Reynard Motorsport|Reynard]]\n| [[Ford-Cosworth]]\n|align=center|5\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"|6\n| [[Chip Ganassi Racing|Ganassi]]\n|-\n| [[1995 Indianapolis 500|1995]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Ford-Cosworth]]\n|align=center|4\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|25\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[2001 Indianapolis 500|2001]]\n| [[Dallara]]\n| [[Oldsmobile]]\n|