nd:#DFFFDF;\"|5\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1985 Indianapolis 500|1985]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center|15\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"|8\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1986 Indianapolis 500|1986]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"|3\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"|6\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1987 Indianapolis 500|1987]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center|9\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|29\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1988 Indianapolis 500|1988]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n|align=center|10\n|align=center style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"|4\n| [[Kraco Racing|Kraco]]\n|-\n| [[1989 Indianapolis 500|1989]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=center|21\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|17\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1990 Indianapolis 500|1990]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=center|5\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|20\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1991 Indianapolis 500|1991]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=center|5\n|align=center style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"|2\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1992 Indianapolis 500|1992]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Ford-Cosworth]]\n|align=center|6\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|''13''\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[1994 Indianapolis 500|1994]]\n| [[Reynard Motorsport|Reynard]]\n| [[Ford-Cosworth]]\n|align=center|5\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"|6\n| [[Chip Ganassi Racing|Ganassi]]\n|-\n| [[1995 Indianapolis 500|1995]]\n| [[Lola Cars|Lola]]\n| [[Ford-Cosworth]]\n|align=center|4\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|25\n| [[Newman/Haas Racing|Newman/Haas]]\n|-\n| [[2001 Indianapolis 500|2001]]\n| [[Dallara]]\n| [[Oldsmobile]]\n|align=center|21\n|align=center style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"|3\n| [[Andretti Green|Team Green]]\n|-\n| [[2002 Indianapolis 500|2002]]\n| [[Dallara]]\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=center|25\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"|7\n| [[Andretti Green|Team Green]]\n|-\n| [[2003 Indianapolis 500|2003]]\n| [[Dallara]]\n| [[Honda]]\n|align=center|13\n|align=center style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"|27\n| [[Andretti Green]]\n|-\n| [[2006 Indianapolis 500|2006]]\n| [[Dallara]]\n| [[Honda]]\n|align=center|13\n|align=center style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"|3\n| [[Andretti Green]]\n|-\n| [[2007 Indianapolis 500|2007]]\n| [[Dallara]]\n| [[Honda]]\n|align=center|11\n|align=center style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"|13\n| [[Andretti Green]]\n|}\n\n==Further reading==\n\n*Michael Andretti, Robert Carver & Douglas Carver. '' Michael Andretti at Indianapolis ''. Simon & Schuster. {{ISBN|978-0671752965}}\n\n== See also ==\n\n* ''[[Michael Andretti's World GP]]'', a video game that licensed his name\n\n== References ==\n\n{{reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category|Michael Andretti}}\n\n* [http://www.andretti.com/ The Official Andretti Family Website]\n* {{Racing-Reference driver|Michael_Andretti}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20120512065448/http://f1rejects.com/centrale/andretti/index.html Article on Andretti's F1 career]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110724044601/http://www.thegreatest33.com/default.aspx#selecteddrivers?s=michael_andretti The Greatest 33]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-sports}}\n{{succession box|title=[[Super Vee|Robert Bosch US Formula Super Vee]]<br>[[Champion]]|before=[[Al Unser, Jr.]]|after=[[Ed Pimm]]|years=1982}}\n{{succession box|title=[[Atlantic Championship|FIA Formula Mondial North American Cup]]<br>[[Champion]]|before=[[Dave McMillan (driver)|Dave McMillan]]|after=[[Dan Marvin]]|years=1983}}\n{{succession box | title = [[Indianapolis 500 Rookie of the Year|Indianapolis 500]]<br>[[Indianapolis 500 Rookie of the Year|Rookie of the Year]]| years = [[1984 Indianapolis 500|1984]]<small> with:</small><br />